msgid ""
"%1$s and %2$s are the group-level effect size and standard deviation, "
"respectively."
msgstr ""
"%1$s と %2$s およびs は、それぞれグループレベルの効果量と標準偏差です。"

msgid "%s is the group-level effect size."
msgstr "%s はグループレベルの効果量です."

msgid "Bayes factor of the random effects H%1$s over the fixed effects H%1$s."
msgstr "ランダム効果 H%1$s に対する固定効果H%1$s のベイズ因子。"

msgid ""
"Posterior estimates are based on the models that assume an effect to be "
"present. The Bayes factor is based on all four models: fixed effects H%2$s & "
"random effects H%2$s over the fixed effects H%1$s & random effects H%1$s."
msgstr ""
"事後推定値は、効果が存在すると仮定したモデルに基づいています。ベイズ因子は、"
"固定効果 H%1$sおよびランダム効果Hs に対する固定効果 H%2$s およびランダム効果"
"H%2$s のすべての4つのモデルに基づいています。"

msgid ""
"Model averaged posterior estimates for %3$s are not yet available, but will "
"be added in the future. The Bayes factor is based on all four models: random "
"effects H%1$s & H%2$s over the fixed effects H%1$s & H%2$s."
msgstr ""
"Model averaged posterior estimates for %3$s are not yet available, but will "
"be added in the future. The Bayes factor is based on all four models: random "
"effects H%1$s & H%2$s over the fixed effects H%1$s & H%2$s."

msgid ""
"Bayes factor of the (unconstrained/constrained) random effects H%1$s over "
"the fixed effects H%1$s."
msgstr ""
"固定効果 H%1$s に対する (制約なし/制約あり) 変量効果 H%1$s のベイズファク"
"ター."

msgid "Bayes factor of the fixed effects H%1$s over the random effects H%1$s."
msgstr ""
"変量効果 H%1$s に対する (制約なし/制約あり) 固定効果 H%1$s のベイズファク"
"ター."

msgid ""
"Model averaged posterior estimates are based on the models that assume an "
"effect to be present. The Bayes factor is based on all four models: fixed "
"effects H%1$s & random effects H%1$s over the fixed effects H%2$s & random "
"effects H%2$s."
msgstr ""
"モデル平均事後推定値は効果が存在すると仮定したモデルに基づいています。ベイズ"
"ファクターは、4つのモデルすべてに基づいています: 固定効果H%2$s & 変量効果"
"H%2$s よりも固定効果H%1$s & 変量効果 H%2$s."

msgid ""
"Model averaged posterior estimates for %3$s are not yet available, but will "
"be added in the future. The Bayes factor is based on all four models: fixed "
"effects H%1$s & H%2$s over the random effects H%1$s & H%2$s."
msgstr ""
"%3$s におけるモデル平均事後推定値はまだありませんが、今後追加される予定です。"
"ベイズファクターは、4つのモデルすべてに基づいています: 変量効果H%1$s & H%2$s"
"よりも固定効果H%1$s & H%2$s."

msgid ""
"Bayes factor of the fixed effects H%1$s over the (unconstrained/constrained) "
"random effects H%1$s."
msgstr ""
"（制約なし/制約付き）変量効果H%1$sに対する固定効果H%1$sのベイズファクター."

msgid ""
"Bayes factor of the ordered effects H%1$s over the fixed effects H%2$s. The "
"Bayes factor for the ordered effects H%1$s versus the unconstrained (random) "
"effects H%1$s model is %3$.3f."
msgstr ""
"固定効果 H%2$s に対する順序効果 H%1$s のベイズファクター. 制約のない(変量)効"
"果 H%1$s モデルに対する順序効果 H%1$s のベイズファクターは %3$.3f."

msgid ""
"Bayes factor of the fixed effects H%2$s over the ordered effects H%1$s. The "
"Bayes factor for the unconstrained (random) effects H%1$s versus the ordered "
"effects H%1$s model is %3$.3f."
msgstr ""
"順序効果 H%1$s に対する固定効果 H%2$s のベイズファクター. 順序効果 H%1$s モデ"
"ルに対する制約のない(変量)効果 H%1$s のベイズファクターは %3$.3f."

